bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "easyshare"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "easyshare"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
axum_typed_multipart = "0.13.0"
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
log = "0.4"
simple_logger = "5"
thiserror = "2"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.7"
features = ["macros"]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.4.11"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.29"
features = ["futures-sink"]

[dependencies.maud]
version = "0.26.0"
features = ["axum"]

[dependencies.object_store]
version = "0.11.0"
features = ["aws"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.5"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.6"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.6.1"
features = ["v4"]
